WorkItem.Description:
I am using the 0.9 alpha preview and have noticed a discrepancy between the 0.9 specification and the preview.

The following example should alert "Large", but alerts "Undefined" - described in the final example of section 9.1 (page 87).

```
enum TShirtSize {
    Small,
    Medium,
    Large
}

var mySize = TShirtSize.Large;

var test = TShirtSize[mySize];

alert(TShirtSize[test]);
```
